---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import HeaderSmall from "../components/HeaderSmall.astro";

import CustomFullImageHero from "../components/custom/CustomFullImageHero.astro";
import CustomSectionHeader from "../components/custom/CustomSectionHeader.astro";

import Graphics from "../assets/images/grahics.webp";
import Code from "../assets/images/code.webp";
import Tracking from "../assets/images/tracking.webp";
import DeskTop from "../assets/images/desk_view.webp";
const title = "Services";
const subtitle =
  "We take care of all your website needs so you can focus on growing your business.";
---

<Layout title="Services" description="Services offered by Sublime UX">
  <div>
    <!--  -->
    <CustomFullImageHero
      title={title}
      subtitle={subtitle}
      showButtons={false}
    />
  </div>
  <main class="mx-4 lg:mx-16">
    <div
      class="my-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row content-start md:space-x-6"
      id="design"
    >
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <CustomSectionHeader
          title="Design"
          subtitle="The importance of design for your business"
        />
        <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden rounded-md shadow-sm">
          <Image
            src={Graphics}
            width={800}
            height={499}
            alt="Graphic design and visual identity services by Sublime UX"
            class="object-contain"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:max-w-2xl mt-8">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          Why a High-Performance Website is Your Greatest Sales Asset
        </h4>
        <p class="text-md">
          Your website isn't just a digital brochure; it's the most critical
          stage of your sales funnel. It either converts visitors into customers
          or it leaks money. We design and build sites with one goal in mind: to
          turn clicks into clients.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">Lead Generation & Conversion</h4>
        <p>
          Most websites are built for "traffic," but we build for <strong
            >conversion</strong
          >. We architect a user journey that is frictionless and intuitive.
          This means a clear path from landing on a page to signing up, buying,
          or calling. By making it simple for people to take action, we
          dramatically increase your lead volume and revenue, ensuring every
          visitor has a purpose.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">Authority & Trust</h4>
        <p>
          In a crowded market, trust is currency. Your brand needs to look like
          a category leader, not an afterthought. We design websites that
          instantly communicate credibility and authority. Every element—from
          the visual design to the messaging—is crafted to build confidence and
          make your audience feel like they've found the professional solution
          to their problem.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div
      class="my-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row content-start md:space-x-6"
      id="seo"
    >
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <CustomSectionHeader
          title="SEO"
          subtitle="What is Search Engine Optimization (SEO)"
        />
        <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden rounded-md shadow-sm">
          <Image
            src={Code}
            width={800}
            height={499}
            alt="Web development and code optimization services by Sublime UX"
            class="object-contain"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:max-w-2xl mt-8">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">The Engine for SEO</h4>
        <p>
          You can't sell to people who can't find you. Your website is the
          foundation of your entire online visibility strategy. We build sites
          that are technically sound and optimized to rank high on Google from
          day one. This isn't a "nice-to-have"; it's a mandatory step to secure
          your spot on the first page, capture organic traffic, and become a
          dominant force in your market.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">Seamless Mobile Experience</h4>
        <p>
          With over half of all web traffic coming from mobile devices, a clunky
          mobile site is a revenue killer. We ensure your website delivers a
          flawless experience on every device. This keeps potential customers
          engaged, reduces your bounce rate, and prevents you from losing
          business to competitors with better mobile experiences. We don't just
          "make it mobile-friendly"; we build it for the user in their pocket,
          turning their device into a sales terminal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div
      class="my-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row content-start space-x-6"
      id="growth"
    >
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <CustomSectionHeader
          title="Growth"
          subtitle="Boost Your Business by Optimizing Conversions"
        />
        <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden rounded-md shadow-sm">
          <Image
            src={Tracking}
            width={800}
            height={499}
            alt="SEO and growth tracking services by Sublime UX"
            class="object-contain"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-none lg:max-w-2xl mt-8">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          Stop Wasting Traffic. Start Making Money.
        </h4>
        <p class="text-md">
          You've invested time and money getting people to your website. But if
          they're not turning into customers, you're just paying for a revolving
          door. You don't have a traffic problem; you have a <strong
            >conversion problem</strong
          >. We fix that.
        </p>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          What We Do: Turn Clicks Into Customers
        </h4>
        <p class="text-md">
          Instead of building a website and hoping for the best, we
          reverse-engineer the buying process. We use data, not guesswork, to
          find out exactly where your visitors are getting stuck and why they're
          leaving. Our goal is simple: to make your website an unstoppable sales
          engine. We get you more leads and more sales <strong
            >without spending a single extra dollar on ads</strong
          >.
        </p>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-medium my-4">
          How We Do It: The Conversion Machine
        </h4>
        <p>
          We've got a proven process to optimize your website for maximum
          return.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-3 my-4">
          <li class="">
            <strong>Audit Your Funnel:</strong> We dig into your analytics to pinpoint
            exactly where you're losing money. We identify the bottlenecks and friction
            points that are killing your conversions.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Remove the Barriers:</strong> We simplify your website and messaging
            to make it effortless for a customer to take action. This means irresistible
            offers, crystal-clear calls-to-action, and a user experience so smooth
            they can't help but convert.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Build Trust & Authority:</strong> We use customer proof, data,
            and powerful storytelling to make your brand the obvious choice. When
            your visitors feel confident and understood, they are far more likely
            to buy.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

